<P>
THE INJUSTICE OF TRUMP'S NEW BUDGET 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Re "Los Angeles on $450,000? No Way, (July 3)": There can never be peace in 
this favored land until there is justice. Tell me if you can where is the 
justice in Donald Trump having $450,000 to spend every single month when an 
army of children cry themselves to sleep every night because it hurts to be 
hungry. 
</P>
<P>
GLADYS FOREMAN 
</P>
<P>
Los Angeles 
</P>
