<HEADLINE>
<P>
MORNING REPORT: RADIO 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
By GREG BRAXTON, Arts and entertainment reports from The Times, national and 
international news services and the nation's press. 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Summer Classics: Los Angeles Philharmonic concerts return to the airwaves at 9 
this morning on KCRW-FM (89.9), with a repeat at 10 tonight on KUSC-FM (91.5). 
The 13-week Friday series represents a unique cooperation between public-radio 
stations on two different networks. GREG BRAXTON 
</P>
