<TEXT>
<P>
The body of an unidentified woman was found at the archery range in Balboa 
Park's Palm Canyon Park about 9:15 a.m. Thursday, Homicide Lt. Jim Duncan said. 
</P>
<P>
The cause of death was undetermined, Duncan said. "There were no stab wounds, 
no obvious signs of trauma." An autopsy will be performed. 
</P>
<P>
Duncan said the woman was wearing jeans, a T-shirt and a sweat shirt. Her age 
was estimated at 35 to 40. 
</P>
<P>
