<TEXT>
<P>
Well, my triple streak ended at one in a row when none of my horses in the 
seventh, eighth and ninth races could find the winner's circle, so it cost me 
$20 of my bankroll. 
</P>
<P>
However, I am going to stick with the triples, making a $15 bet on Warrior and 
Circumsteller in the first to Ono Gummo and Superbe King in the second to Fire 
Back in the third and a $10 straight triple Warrior-Ono Gummo-Fire Back. 
</P>
<P>
Bob's Thursday Bankroll $1,921 
</P>
<P>
Thursday's Loss $20 
</P>
<P>
Current Bankroll 1,901 
</P>
<P>
Break up the computer! For the fourth Thursday in a row and the fifth day in 
the last six, the computer continued its winning ways, netting a $70 profit 
from its $100 wager on Putting ($3.40) in the fifth. 
</P>
<P>
For today, the computer will bet a $40 exacta from Tasteful T.V. to Dame 
Rousara in the seventh and a $20 exacta reversing the two. 
