Angeles Times; Photo, Off-duty Torrance firefighter Joe Neese carrying hoses up 
a driveway ; Photo, Palos Verdes Estates resident John Boyt hoses a neighbor's 
home, despite a drop in water pressure. BRIAN VANDER BRUG / Los Angeles Times; 
Photo, And a firefighter spraying embers ED COMPEAN / Los Angeles Times 
